728788f-a.title: Richmond: Delafield Avenue - Clove Road
728788f-a.text:
752 Delafield Ave., adjoining the S.W. corner of Clove Road.
This house was owned by one named Smith according to Beers' map of
1874. Later, it was the property of A.A. Mitchell (1898-1907 maps).
This is a set of two views taken the same day.
July 2, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
